      "description": "Non-planar integral family NP for two-loop mixed QCD-EW corrections to $gg \\to Hg$. Non-planar topology with crossed massive vector-boson propagators ($D_4,D_6$) and massless propagators ($D_1,D_2,D_3,D_5,D_7$). 9 denominators (7 propagators + 2 ISPs: $D_8=(l-p_1)^2-m_V^2$, $D_9=(k-p_1-p_3)^2$). 18 non-planar master integrals. Kinematics: $s=(p_1+p_2)^2$, $t=(p_1+p_3)^2$, $u=(p_2+p_3)^2$, $s+t+u=m_h^2$; $p_1^2=p_2^2=p_3^2=0$, $p_4^2=m_h^2$. Paper label: NP. Defined in Table 1 and eq. (2.4).",
